<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-3671] Add a TypeTokenFilter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3671</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be convenient to have a TypeTokenFilter that filters tokens by its type, either with an exclude or include list. This might be a stupid thing to provide for people who use Lucene directly, but it would be very useful to later expose it to Solr and other Lucene-backed search solutions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
